graph LR
    KUBEFLOW[Kubeflow Notebook Controllers]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    KUBEFLOW -->|container platform| K8S[Kubernetes 0.33.7+<br/>OpenShift 4.19+]
    KUBEFLOW -->|controller framework| CTRLRT[controller-runtime 0.21.0]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    KUBEFLOW -.->|VirtualService ingress| ISTIO[Istio<br/>optional]
    KUBEFLOW -.->|webhook certs| CERTMGR[cert-manager /<br/>OpenShift Service CA<br/>optional]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    KUBEFLOW -->|pipeline integration| DSPA[Data Science Pipelines<br/>DataSciencePipelinesApplication CRD]
    KUBEFLOW -->|user auth| OAUTH[OpenShift OAuth<br/>OAuth Clients]
    KUBEFLOW -->|external access| ROUTES[OpenShift Routes<br/>Route CRD]
    KUBEFLOW -->|gateway ingress| GWAPI[Gateway API<br/>HTTPRoute, ReferenceGrant]
    KUBEFLOW -->|container images| IMGSTREAM[OpenShift ImageStreams<br/>ImageStream CRD]
    KUBEFLOW -.->|feature store| FEAST[Feast<br/>ConfigMap<br/>optional]

    %% Integration Points
    DASHBOARD[ODH Dashboard] -->|create notebooks| KUBEFLOW
    PIPELINES[Data Science Pipelines] -->|auto-deploy models| KUBEFLOW
    KUBEFLOW -->|exposes metrics| PROMETHEUS[Prometheus]

    %% External Services
    KUBEFLOW -->|image pull| REGISTRY[Container Registries<br/>quay.io, registry.redhat.io]
    KUBEFLOW -->|API operations| K8SAPI[Kubernetes API Server]

    %% Service Mesh Integration
    SERVICEMESH[Service Mesh] -.->|mTLS sidecars| KUBEFLOW

    %% Styling
    style KUBEFLOW fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% External Dependencies
    style K8S fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style CTRLRT fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style ISTIO fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style CERTMGR fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    %% Internal ODH
    style DSPA fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style OAUTH fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style ROUTES fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style GWAPI fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style IMGSTREAM fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style FEAST fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style DASHBOARD fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style PIPELINES fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style PROMETHEUS fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style SERVICEMESH fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    %% External Services
    style REGISTRY fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style K8SAPI fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,color:#000
